c\u00fan]], Quintana Roo (Consular Agency)\n** [[Mazatl\u00e1n]], Sinaloa (Consular Agency)\n** [[Oaxaca City]], Oaxaca (Consular Agency)\n** [[Piedras Negras, Coahuila]] (Consular Agency)\n** [[Playa del Carmen]], Quintana Roo (Consular Agency)\n** [[Puerto Vallarta, Jalisco]] (Consular Agency)\n** [[San Miguel de Allende]], Guanajuato (Consular Agency)\n*{{NIC}}\n** [[Managua]] (Embassy)\n*{{PAN}}\n** [[Panama City]] (Embassy)\n*{{PRY}}\n** [[Asunci\u00f3n]] (Embassy)\n*{{PER}}\n** [[Lima]] (Embassy)\n** [[Cusco]] (Consular Agency)\n*{{SUR}}\n** [[Paramaribo]] (Embassy)\n*{{TTO}}\n** [[Port of Spain]] (Embassy)\n*{{URY}}\n** [[Montevideo]] (Embassy)\n*{{VEN}}\n** [[Caracas]] ([[Embassy of the United States, Caracas|Embassy]]) Temporary limited\n** [[Maracaibo]] (Consular Agency) Temporary Limited\n{{div col end}}\n\n<gallery widths=\"200px\" heights=\"200px\">\nFile:US Embassy in Bogota, Colombia.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[Bogota]]\nFile:Embaixada USA Brasil 01.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[Bras\u00edlia]]\nFile:American Embassy in Bridgetown-2.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[Bridgetown]]\nFile:U.S. Flag Flaps Outside U.S. Embassy in Havana, Cuba (25998479275).jpg|[[Embassy of the United States, Havana|U.S. Embassy in Havana]]\nFile:US Embassy in La Paz.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[La Paz]]\nFile:USEmbassyDF.JPG|[[Embassy of the United States, Mexico City|U.S. Embassy in Mexico City]]\nFile:American Embassy in Ottawa.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[Ottawa]]\nFile:paramaribo district 14.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[Paramaribo]]\nFile:USEmbassy PortofSpain.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[Port of Spain]]\nFile:US Consulate-General in Quebec City-3.jpg|U.S. Consulate-General in [[Quebec City]]\nFile:U.S. Embassy in Ecuador.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[Quito]]\nFile:American Embassy in San Jose.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[San Jos\u00e9, Costa Rica|San Jos\u00e9]]\nFile:Embassy of the United States of America in San Salvador, El Salvador.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[San Salvador]]\nFile:US Embassy in Tegucigapa 2.jpg|U.S. Embassy in [[Tegucigalpa]]\nFile:Consulate of the United States in Toronto.JPG|U.S. Consulate-General in [[Toronto]]\n</gallery>\n\n==Asia==\nThe U.S. has embassies in all countries it recognizes apart from Bhutan, Iran, Maldives, North Korea, Syria and Yemen. It has 'interest sections' in other nation's embassies in Iran and Syria. It also has a ''de facto'' embassy in Taiwan. \n{{Div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*{{AFG}}\n** [[Kabul]] ([[Embassy of the United States, Kabul|Embassy]])\n*{{ARM}}\n** [[Yerevan]] ([[Embassy of the United States, Yerevan|Embassy]])\n*{{AZE}}\n** [[Baku]] (Embassy)\n*{{BHR}}\n** [[Manama]] ([[Embassy of the United States, Manama|Embassy]])\n*{{BGD}}\n** [[Dhaka]] ([[Embassy of the United States, Dhaka|Embassy]])\n*{{BRN}}\n** [[Bandar Seri Begawan]] (Embassy)\n*{{KHM}}\n** [[Phnom Penh]] (Embassy)\n*{{CHN}}\n** [[Beijing]] ([[Embassy of the United States, Beijing|Embassy]])\n** [[Chengdu]] ([[U.S. Consulate General, Chengdu|Consulate General]])\n** [[Guangzhou]] ([[Consulate General of the United States, Guangzhou|Consulate General]])\n** [[Hong Kong]] ([[Consulate General of the United States, Hong Kong and Macau|Consulate General]])\n** [[Shanghai]] ([[U.S. Consulate General, Shanghai|Consulate General]])\n** [[Shenyang]] ([[U.S. Consulate General, Shenyang|Consulate General]])\n** [[Wuhan]] ([[U.S. Consulate General, Wuhan|Consulate General]])\n*{{Flag|East Timor}}\n** [[Dili]] (Embassy)\n*{{GEO}}\n** [[Tbilisi]] ([[Embassy of the United States, Tbilisi|Embassy]])\n*{{IND}}\n** [[New Delhi]] ([[Embassy of the United States, New Delhi|Embassy]])\n** [[Chennai]] ([[Consulate General of the United States, Chennai|Consulate General]])\n** [[Hyderabad, Andhra Pradesh|Hyderabad]] ([[Consulate General of the United States, Hyderabad|Consulate General]])\n** [[Kolkata]] ([[Consulate General of the United States, Kolkata|Consulate General]])\n** [[Mumbai]] ([[Consulate General of the United States, Mumbai|Consulate General]])\n*{{IDN}}\n** [[Jakarta]] ([[Embassy of the Uni